# Native std.ui provider

[signal, element, textNode, signalText, showSignal, emit](std/ui/primitives.ssc)
[readFile](std/fs.ssc)
[pathJoin](std/os.ssc)

```scalascript
val name = signal("name", "Grace")
val visible = signal("visible", true)
name.set("Ada")
emit(
  element("main", Map("id" -> "app", "class" -> "card"), Map(), List(
    element("h1", Map(), Map(), List(textNode("Hi <native>"))),
    signalText(name),
    showSignal(visible,
      element("span", Map(), Map(), List(textNode("shown"))),
      textNode("hidden"))
  )),
  args(0)
)
println(readFile(pathJoin(args(0), "index.html")))
```
